      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "INDIAN STAR (1) has been hard to follow lately, running sixth (32.03) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at Ballarat. Better than last run and makes appeal this time. DRIP DRIP (6) was narrowly beaten when placing two back but missed the frame latest finishing fifth (30.96) in a Maiden at The Meadows. Can find the frame this time. HARRY TIME (4) eye-catching debut run after settling well back but winding up strongly into the frame when third (25.98) at Ballarat over 450m. Expected to do much better this time. LEKTRA KNIGHT (8) makes debut for the Sharon Bradley kennel. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Can feature with the right run.",
